<emphasis id="AC1CE8AA007A6B437848A7D122D1D35D" bold="true" pageId="0" pageNumber="81">d</emphasis>
vertical section through an apothecium 
<emphasis id="7EBCE9E8002F952B5FE50EE82F650591" bold="true" pageId="0" pageNumber="81">e</emphasis>
covering stroma 
<emphasis id="CBD3288BF221CA37B9124EC74EF856B9" bold="true" pageId="0" pageNumber="81">f</emphasis>
triangular space in section between the covering stroma and basal stroma 
<emphasis id="92E481A73FF52D356F1E7E18398F6002" bold="true" pageId="0" pageNumber="81">g</emphasis>
basal stroma 
